## 5. RBAC Enforcement (⚠️ CRITICAL — Strictly Enforced)

| Role | Permissions |
|---|---|
| **Customer** | Access `/cart`, `/checkout`, `/account/orders`, `/account/profile`. Can only view own orders via `/api/orders/*`. |
| **Admin Branch** | **MUST ONLY SEE ORDERS FROM THEIR ASSIGNED BRANCH**. Access `/admin/orders` with automatic `branchId` filter. Can verify pickup codes. Receives real-time notifications for new orders in their branch. |
| **Admin HQ** | Can see **ALL ORDERS FROM ALL BRANCHES**. Branch filter is available in UI. Can view all order details but **does NOT have pickup code verification UI** (read-only for status actions). |

**Implementation:** Enforce at API route level using `withAuth` pattern from `apps/admin/src/lib/auth-guard.ts`. Branch admins MUST have their `branchId` checked against `orders.branchId` on **EVERY** query. Never rely on UI hiding alone.

