## 6. Flow Diagrams (Mermaid)

### 6.1 Overall Checkout to Fulfillment Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Customer browses products] --> B["Add to Cart\nenforce 1 cart = 1 branch"]
    B --> C[Go to /cart]
    C --> D[Click Checkout]
    D --> E["Step 1: Contact Info\nphone + email"]
    E --> F["Step 2: Pickup Branch & Time\nvalidate operating hours"]
    F --> G["Step 3: QRIS Payment\nMidtrans Snap"]
    G --> H["Place Order → status=pending_payment"]
    H --> I[Redirect to Midtrans]
    I --> J{Payment Result}
    J -->|Success| K["Webhook: payment_status=paid\nAuto-generate pickup_code\nstatus=ready_for_pickup"]
    J -->|Fail| L[status=cancelled]
    K --> M["Email #1 sent to customer\nOrder + Payment + Pickup Code"]
    K --> N["Admin Branch notified\nWebSocket/SSE"]
    N --> O[Admin prepares order]
    O --> P[Customer arrives at branch]
    P --> Q[States code to admin]
    Q --> R[Admin inputs code]
    R --> S{Code valid?}
    S -->|Yes| T[Order status = completed]
    T --> U["Email #2 sent\nOrder Completed"]
    S -->|No| V["Error: Invalid code"]
    U --> W["Customer & Admin can inquiry\ntransaction history"]
```

### 6.2 Cart Branch Enforcement Logic

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[User clicks Add to Cart] --> B{Cart exists?}
    B -->|No| C[Create cart with branchId]
    B -->|Yes| D{carts.branchId == item.branchId?}
    D -->|Yes| E[Add or update cartItems]
    D -->|No| F[Return CART_BRANCH_MISMATCH]
    F --> G[Show branch switch modal]
    G -->|Confirm| H[Clear cart and set new branchId]
    G -->|Cancel| I[Abort add to cart]
    H --> E
    E --> J[Validate stock vs branchStocks]
```

### 6.3 Admin Order Status Management

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A(Admin opens order detail page) --> B{Current Status}
    B -->|pending_payment| C(Read only - Waiting for payment)
    B -->|processing| D(Read only - Order being prepared)
    B -->|ready_for_pickup| E(Input customer pickup code)
    E --> F(Admin types code and clicks Verify)
    F --> G{Code matches pickupCode?}
    G -->|Yes| H(Update status to completed)
    H --> I(Send Email 2 - Order Completed)
    G -->|No| J(Show error - Invalid pickup code)
    B -->|completed| K(Read only view)
```

### 6.4 Midtrans Webhook Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Customer
    participant M as Midtrans
    participant WH as /api/webhooks/midtrans
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant N as Nodemailer/Gmail SMTP
    participant WS as WebSocket/SSE

    C->>M: Scan QRIS & Pay
    M-->>WH: POST callback + signature
    WH->>WH: Verify SHA256 signature
    alt Valid & status=settlement
        WH->>DB: Update payment_status=paid, status=processing
        WH->>DB: Deduct branchStocks
        WH->>DB: Generate pickupCode, status=ready_for_pickup
        WH->>N: Queue Email #1 (Pickup Ready)
        WH->>WS: Emit to admin branch room
    else Invalid signature or failed
        WH->>DB: Update payment_status=failed, status=cancelled
        WH->>DB: Restore branchStocks
    end
    WH-->>M: HTTP 200 OK
```

